                <h2>Mitigation: Immediate Actions Required</h2>
                
                <h3>1. Patch Immediately</h3>
                <p><strong>Windows Update:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Settings ‚Üí Windows Update ‚Üí Check for updates</li>
